resumes.summary: Creative and detail-oriented Web Developer with a BTech in Computer Science Engineering and hands-on experience in MEARN stack development through an intensive internship at Luminar Technolab. Adept at building responsive, user-friendly interfaces using modern JavaScript and Tailwind CSS, with a strong focus on animation, interactivity, and polished design. Skilled in debugging, DOM manipulation, and deploying React applications to GitHub Pages. Passionate about blending code and design to deliver engaging user experiences, and actively preparing for tech interviews with a portfolio of dynamic, real-world projects.
